title: Jenkins and Jonez - Can You Believe Snoop Dogg Smoked Weed???
itunes:title: Jenkins and Jonez - Can You Believe Snoop Dogg Smoked Weed???
description:
The guys discuss the Super Bowl commercials and halftime show including why people are surprised that Snoop Dogg smoked weed before the performance. Then they laugh at James Harden rolling his eyes at Kevin Durant, talk about how the Bucks are still the favorites in the East, and start “serious or unserious”.
